                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JAMES SMITH</hi> (32)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18621027-1095-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18621027-1095-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18621027-1095-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>, Unlawfully conspiring to cheat and defraud <persName id="t18621027-name-337" type="victimName">
